    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy (NIH within 18% of experiment, RH = 0.87 < 1.0 at worst-case condition). Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. The credibility evidence package supports the regulatory claim that the CFD model can reliably identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
